extendedInfo.description: Discover a peaceful forest teeming with wildlife and surrounded by natural beauty every time you use your device.Sunlight filters through the trees as a gentle breeze rustles the leaves. Pause for reflection at the path while birds flutter past and deer graze contentedly in the rich foliage and quiet solitude of the undisturbed woods.Choose the Natural theme, and your forest becomes pristine as you discover a cascading waterfall. Or, rest at your private cabin before setting out on a hike through the woods at the pathway signs - it's all up to you!Interact with an owl or birds and watch the deer gaze at the forest. Customize the wildlife, flowers, cabin, signs, grass, waterfall, and much more!Several optional add-on packs are also available for purchase, allowing you to choose the features most meaningful to you:* The âField Packâ allows you to explore a completely new scene featuring a field of tall waving grass, butterflies, a rabbit, additional deer, and more.* In the âStream Packâ, just one of the new features is a babbling brook winding through the forest while a buck sips from the clear waters in changing weather conditions, fish, squirrels, and more.* The âCustomization Packâ features even more personalization options such as your own text and images in the scene, dynamic time of day, fireflies at night, and more.This visually stunning live wallpaper is true 3D with hand-crafted artwork. Our wallpapers feature silky-smooth animations while conserving your battery life and works great with phones, tablets, or any device that supports live wallpapers.

reviews.title: Dual Boot has the BEST live wallpapers!
reviews.comment: Edit: The new update. The new animals (rabbits, owls, squirrels) are adorable! I\'ve been looking for a forest live wallpaper and I hadn\'t found one I liked yet. Well dualboot has done it again. Beautiful live wallpaper. I hope they release the expansion packs soon!
reviews.author: Amanda Willen

reviews.title: DualBoot does it again!
reviews.comment: Another amazing live wallpaper by this dev! Very serene, love the deer animations - their movements are quite realistic. The additional surprise of Bigfoot ranks this as a favorite! When you see the footprints look for him peeking out from behind a tree in the scene next to the last (cabin). Make this your wallpaper, you won\'t regret it.

reviews.title: Love this app
reviews.comment: Beautiful adaptable scenery, a nice mini game customizing the forest scenes.  I also like that you can buy or not buy extras as you need.  Cheap price for such a nice background app.

reviews.title: Love animals, great animation
